                     <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17761204-1-victim47 t17761204-1-viclabel2"></join>, on the <rs id="t17761204-1-cd3" type="crimeDate">18th of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17761204-1-off1 t17761204-1-cd3"></join>, about the hour of two in the night, and stealing a pair of brown thread stockings, value 1 s. a pair of silver shoe-buckles, value 5 s. and 7 s. in money numbered, the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17761204-1-victim49" type="victimName">
                           Edward
